Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.55,0:00:53.42,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}どうしたら あなたに愛を刻めるんだろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.98,0:01:06.58,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}知らない気持ちばかり 覚えたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.58,0:01:09.81,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}忘れかたも教えて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.84,0:01:16.00,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}言葉だけじゃなくてさ 震える指の温度から
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.14,0:01:22.60,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}それは誰の希望? 私から溢れ出した願いの雫（DROP）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.60,0:01:26.17,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}消えても 消えても 生まれてくるけど
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.27,0:01:29.17,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}答えなき酷い未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.56,0:01:35.30,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}何回目の明日が来るのか わからない夜なら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.30,0:01:39.90,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}名前を呼ばれたい だって胸が痛い
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.90,0:01:43.88,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}痛くて張り裂けそうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.34,0:01:51.57,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}どうしたら あなたに愛を刻めるんだろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.72,0:01:57.44,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}私がいつか 空に溶け去る前に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.44,0:02:05.00,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}強い想いで いまを守りたくなった
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.00,0:02:11.86,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}理由は あなたをもっと見ていたいから…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.55,0:00:53.42,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}如何才能在你心中  銘刻下我的愛意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.98,0:01:06.58,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}是你  讓我體會到無數不曾知曉的情感
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.58,0:01:09.81,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}告訴我該如何忘記吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.84,0:01:16.00,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}不要只是開口  用你顫抖的手指的溫度告訴我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.14,0:01:22.60,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}又是誰的希望  讓我眼眶中的淚水決堤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.60,0:01:26.17,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}即便滑落臉龐  消失無蹤  又會聚滿眼眶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.27,0:01:29.17,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}悲慘的未來裡  我尋覓不到答案
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.56,0:01:35.30,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}長夜漫漫  不知道要第幾次迎來明天時
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.30,0:01:39.90,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}總想聽到你呼喚我的名字  只因揪緊的心口
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.90,0:01:43.88,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}撕心裂肺的痛苦  叫我不堪忍受
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.34,0:01:51.57,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}如何才能在你心中  銘刻下我的愛意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.72,0:01:57.44,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}不要等到我  化作天邊星辰的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.44,0:02:05.00,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}強烈的思念  催促我守護眼前的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.00,0:02:11.86,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}只因為還想多見到你  哪怕一分一秒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.79,0:22:01.54,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\be10\pos(625,715)}「告訴我 我是誰？」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.54,0:22:06.84,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,84)\be10}你只露出了溫柔的微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.47,0:22:15.64,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\be10}我想 其實並不需要什麼答案
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.64,0:22:18.02,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\be10}那朦朧的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.02,0:22:23.40,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\be10}幸福的觸感 是那麼的柔軟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.40,0:22:27.78,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\be10}對明天的一份掛念 就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.78,0:22:32.66,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\be10}飄上了藍天 消失在視線中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.66,0:22:38.50,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\be10}澄澈的心 知道了何謂喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.50,0:22:42.42,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\be10}最終 也領會了何謂寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.42,0:22:49.51,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\be10}一聲再見 將我們緊緊聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.51,0:22:54.18,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\be10}啊 我要回到有你等候的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.18,0:22:58.85,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\be10}對你的喜歡 竟使我泫然欲泣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.85,0:23:02.86,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\be10}你輕輕告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.86,0:23:06.86,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1134)\be10}歡迎回家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.84,0:20:17.59,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}Skies,where the blue birds fly
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.80,0:20:23.97,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}Clouds where the people place their souls on to
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.51,0:20:30.08,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}Brighter,the sunshines that go through my tears
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.08,0:20:35.51,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}like searching for what heals my sorrows
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.67,0:20:52.66,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}Cry,when the twilight's come
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.53,0:20:59.01,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}Rise,when the people's prayer's melt in to
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.29,0:21:04.53,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}one,to where we'd been together in the sphere
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.74,0:21:09.73,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}I'm searching for where you are,my soul
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.23,0:21:16.65,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}I don't know how to put my heart belongs to you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.93,0:21:22.61,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}I don't know how to love someone except for you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.78,0:21:28.90,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}That is all my world to been had you in my life
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.33,0:21:34.88,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs34}I'll call you all the time
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.84,0:20:17.59,CQCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs40}藍天  青鳥翱翔的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.80,0:20:23.97,CQCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs40}雲朵 寄託靈魂的歸處
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.51,0:20:30.08,CQCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs40}燦爛的陽光  照耀我的眼淚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.08,0:20:35.51,CQCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs40}彷彿在探索  如何療癒我的悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.67,0:20:52.66,CQCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs40}哭泣  總在黎明時分到來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.53,0:20:59.01,CQCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs40}初升  融化了禱告的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.29,0:21:04.53,CQCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs40}星球上  會有片天地留給我和你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.74,0:21:09.73,CQCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs40}我的靈魂  你究竟身在何方?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.23,0:21:16.65,CQCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs40}我不知道  該如何將心交給你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.93,0:21:22.61,CQCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs40}我不知道  除了你還能愛上誰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.78,0:21:28.90,CQCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs40}擁有你  是我生命的全部意義
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.33,0:21:34.88,CQCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an9\fs40}無論何時  我都會呼喚你的名字
